a statistical process to control data coming out of clinical trials.

00:04:04.279 --> 00:04:07.039
Outside of work, I have a number of hats I wear.

00:04:07.039 --> 00:04:11.039
I have way too many children, literally.

00:04:11.039 --> 00:04:14.279
And I also do a lot of creative type of stuff.

00:04:14.279 --> 00:04:21.140
So woodworking, fixing up houses, remodeling kitchens.

00:04:21.140 --> 00:04:23.540
This week, I'm crocheting hats.

00:04:23.540 --> 00:04:25.440
So I'll show you a hat.

00:04:25.440 --> 00:04:31.720
I have a friend who unfortunately passed away of cancer recently, and she used to crochet

